      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented QA plan, version-controlled solver, regression test suite with pass rate ≥95%.",
      "rationale": "Solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022R2) has documented release notes and regression suite. Project-level QA plan covers version control and change management. Achieved level 2: QA plan exists but independent audit not completed; regression suite pass rate 91%, below the 95% threshold required at MRL 5."
    },
