      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) or equivalent code verification demonstrating order-of-accuracy convergence for all governing equations relevant to hemolysis prediction.",
      "rationale": "MMS verification performed for continuity and momentum equations; achieved second-order convergence. Energy and scalar transport equations not independently verified. Achieved level 2 because verification is partial — hemolysis scalar transport equation lacks MMS confirmation."
