      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study completed; GCI on hemolysis index is 1.7%, meeting the 5% threshold. Temporal discretization error estimated at 0.8% for selected time-step. Achieved level 3 because spatial GCI is acceptable but temporal refinement study covers only one operating point, not all five COU conditions."
