      "rationale": "Velocity field is a mechanistically relevant surrogate for hemolysis (shear stress drives power-law model). Linkage documented in sub-model calibration report. Achieved level 3 because surrogate linkage is qualitative; uncertainty in the shear-stress-to-hemolysis transfer function is not propagated into the validation comparison."
