      "rationale": "Convergence criteria set at 1e-4 for all residuals; mass-balance error < 0.1% confirmed. However, no formal round-off error analysis was performed, and iterative convergence not reported individually for all 500 Monte Carlo samples. Flagged as not-assessed at the required level; achieved level 1 (criteria stated but not systematically documented across all runs)."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
