      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent review of simulation setup, boundary conditions, and post-processing scripts; documented checklist with sign-off.",
      "rationale": "No independent review of simulation setup was conducted. Boundary conditions and post-processing scripts reviewed internally by the analyst only. Epistemic gap at MRL 5; achieved level 1."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal justification of turbulence model selection, hemolysis sub-model form, and non-Newtonian blood rheology model with sensitivity analysis demonstrating robustness of hemolysis predictions to model-form choices.",
      "rationale": "k-omega SST turbulence model selected based on prior literature without formal sensitivity analysis. Newtonian blood assumption applied; non-Newtonian effects not assessed. Model-form uncertainty is the dominant epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1: model form choices documented but not justified through sensitivity analysis."
