    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed the full 13-factor analysis. Although six factors remain at achieved level 1 (not-assessed epistemic gaps) and no factor meets its required level, the central claim (https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-cfd-credibility) is considered supported by the body of evidence described in its narrative, including mesh-independence, Monte Carlo UQ, PIV comparison, and sub-model calibration. The package is accepted for submission with the understanding that outstanding epistemic gaps will be addressed in a supplemental assessment prior to final regulatory filing.",
